      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAY PAY PAY (1) has a strong record here with three wins and three placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (20.23) when sixth over 350m at Goulburn in a Mix 2/3. Looks the one to beat with even luck. LOCO STORM (3) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at Richmond Straight in a handy 17.54 beating Loco Dominator. Form from his last run is proving strong. Can make it two on the bounce. SLOY WAVE (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (22.89) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has ability and can atone. LITTLE LINKIN (4) is worth including.",
